FIELD.name: obs_id
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Observation ID- unique identifier of an MWA observation

FIELD.name: starttime
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: GPS Start time of observation

FIELD.name: stoptime
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: GPS Stop time of observation

FIELD.name: duration
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Length of observation in seconds

FIELD.name: starttime_mjd
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: MJD Start time of observation

FIELD.name: stoptime_mjd
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: MJD Stop time of observation

FIELD.name: starttime_utc
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: UTC Start time of observation

FIELD.name: stoptime_utc
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: UTC Stop time of observation

FIELD.name: starttime_mro
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Start time of observation (local MRO time)

FIELD.name: stoptime_mro
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Stop time of observation (local MRO time)

FIELD.name: obsname
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Name of observation

FIELD.name: creator
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Name of the creator of the observation

FIELD.name: modtime
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Last modification date time of the observation (AWST)

FIELD.name: mode
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Observing mode (HW_LFILES/MWAX_CORRELATOR are correlator observations; VOLTAGE_START/VOLTAGE_BUFFER/MWAX_VCS are voltage capture system VCS observations)

FIELD.name: projectid
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Proposal / project identifier

FIELD.name: projectshortname
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Short name of proposal / project identifier

FIELD.name: projectdescription
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Description of proposal / project Identifier

FIELD.name: dataquality
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Data quality code

FIELD.name: dataqualityname
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Data quality description

FIELD.name: dataqualitycomment
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Data quality comment - extra hand written comments on this observations data quality

FIELD.name: deleted_flag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Has this observations files been deleted?

FIELD.name: deletedtime_mro
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Date time of observation deletion (local MRO time)

FIELD.name: vcs_recombined_flag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: For voltage capture system (VCS) observations- has this observation been recombined?

FIELD.name: int_time
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Correlator mode integration time (seconds)

FIELD.name: freq_res
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Correlator mode frequency averaging / fine channel width (kHz)

FIELD.name: ra
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Right ascension (ICRS, J2000.0) (Uses ra_phase if exists, otherwise ra_pointing)

FIELD.name: dec
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Declination (ICRS, J2000.0) (Uses dec_phase if exists, otherwise dec_pointing)

FIELD.name: ra_pointing
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Right ascension (ICRS, J2000.0) of pointing centre at mid-time of the observation (Pointing centre is aligned to the beamformer grid name and grid number)

FIELD.name: dec_pointing
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Declination (ICRS, J2000.0) of pointing centre at mid-time of the observation (Pointing centre is aligned to the beamformer grid name and grid number)

FIELD.name: ra_phase_center
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Right ascension (ICRS, J2000.0) of phase centre at mid-time of the observation

FIELD.name: dec_phase_center
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Declination (ICRS, J2000.0) of phase centre at mid-time of the observation

FIELD.name: azimuth_pointing
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Azimuth of target at mid-time of the observation (decimal degrees)

FIELD.name: elevation_pointing
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Elevation of target at mid-time of the observation (decimal degrees)

FIELD.name: azimuth
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Azimuth, in decimal degrees, of pointing aligned to the beamformer grid name and grid number

FIELD.name: elevation
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Elevation, in decimal degrees, of pointing aligned to the beamformer grid name and grid number

FIELD.name: gal_lat
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Galactic latitude, in decimal degrees, of the phase center (or pointing aligned to the beamformer grid name and grid number if no phase centre)

FIELD.name: gal_long
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Galactic longitude, in decimal degrees, of the phase centre (or pointing aligned to the beamformer grid name and grid number if no phase centre)

FIELD.name: sky_temp
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Sky temperature (K)

FIELD.name: calibration
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Is this an observations used for calibration?

FIELD.name: calibrators
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: If calibration is true what are the calibrator(s) used

FIELD.name: gridpoint_name
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Name of the pointing grid used by this observation

FIELD.name: gridpoint_number
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Gridpoint number for this Observation

FIELD.name: local_sidereal_time_deg
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Local sidereal time (decimal degrees) of observation

FIELD.name: sun_elevation
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Elevation of the Sun at the mid-time of the observation (decimal degrees)

FIELD.name: sun_pointing_distance
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Distance of the Sun from pointing center at mid-time of the observation (decimal degrees)

FIELD.name: jupiter_pointing_distance
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Distance of Jupiter from pointing center at mid-time of the observation (decimal degrees)

FIELD.name: moon_pointing_distance
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Distance of the Moon from pointing center at mid-time of the observation (decimal degrees)

FIELD.name: channel_numbers_csv
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Receiver coarse channel numbers represented as comma separated values

FIELD.name: channel_center_frequencies_mhz_csv
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Receiver coarse channel frequencies, in MHz, represented as comma separated values

FIELD.name: first_channel_number
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: First frequency channel number

FIELD.name: center_channel_number
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Center frequency channel number

FIELD.name: last_channel_number
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Last frequency channel number

FIELD.name: first_channel_lowest_frequency_mhz
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Lower bound frequency of first channel in MHz

FIELD.name: center_frequency_mhz
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Center frequency in MHz

FIELD.name: last_channel_highest_frequency_mhz
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Upper bound frequency of last channel in MHz

FIELD.name: channels_are_contiguous
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Are the coarse channels contiguous?

FIELD.name: channel_count
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Count of channel_width_mhz coarse channels

FIELD.name: channel_width_mhz
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Width of each coarse channel in MHz

FIELD.name: mwa_array_configuration
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The configuration of MWA telescope at the time of this observation

FIELD.name: groupid
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: All observations with this groupid are part of the same observing session

FIELD.name: collection_id
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: This observation is part of a collection with this identifier

FIELD.name: collection_name
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: This observation is part of a collection with this name

FIELD.name: collection_url
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: This observation is part of a collection with this URL

FIELD.name: iono_qa
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Ionosphere QA metric used by the EoR group

FIELD.name: tiles_with_bad_states
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of tiles with bad states

FIELD.name: tiles_with_bad_pointings
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of tiles with bad pointings

FIELD.name: tiles_with_bad_freqs
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of tiles with bad frequencies

FIELD.name: tiles_with_bad_gains
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of tiles with bad gains

FIELD.name: tiles_with_bad_beamshape
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of tiles with bad beamshape (where more than 1 dipole is bad)

FIELD.name: tiles_flagged
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of tiles flagged

FIELD.name: bad_tiles
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total tiles minus good tiles (tiles in bad or unknown state)

FIELD.name: good_tiles
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of good tiles

FIELD.name: total_tiles
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total number of tiles in this observation

FIELD.name: vcs_files_raw_total
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total number of VCS raw files for this observation

FIELD.name: vcs_files_raw_archived
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total number of VCS raw files archived for this observation

FIELD.name: vcs_files_ics_archived
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total number of VCS incoherent sum (ICS) files archived for this observation

FIELD.name: vcs_files_tar_archived
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total number of VCS recombined (tar) files archived for this observation

FIELD.name: gpubox_files_total
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total number of gpubox (visibility) files produced in this observation

FIELD.name: gpubox_files_archived
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total number of gpubox (visibility) files archived for this observation

FIELD.name: flag_files_exist
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Do precomputed RFI flag files exist for this observation (compatible with aoflagger)

FIELD.name: total_archived_data_files
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total files archived for this observation (excluding deleted files, metafits_ppds and flags)

FIELD.name: total_archived_data_bytes
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total bytes archived for this observation (excluding deleted files, metafits_ppds and flags)

FIELD.name: total_archived_files
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total files archived for this observation (excluding deleted files)

FIELD.name: total_archived_bytes
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total bytes archived for this observation (excluding deleted files)

FIELD.name: files_deleted
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total number of files deleted for this observation

FIELD.name: files_deleted_bytes
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total bytes deleted for this observation

FIELD.name: data_files_summary
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Summary of data files. For correlator: gpubox files archived. For VCS: archived raw seconds/archived recombined seconds

FIELD.name: downloads
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total number of downloads of this observation

FIELD.name: first_download_datetime_mro
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Date time the observation was first downloaded (local MRO time)

FIELD.name: last_download_datetime_mro
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Date time of most recent download of this observation (local MRO time)

FIELD.name: days_since_last_download
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Days since last download of this observation

FIELD.name: days_from_obs_to_first_download
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Days elapsed between the observation and first download

FIELD.name: downloaded_bytes
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total bytes downloaded for this observation

FIELD.name: delaymode_name
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Delay mode name (see delaymode_description for info)

FIELD.name: delaymode_description
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Description of the delay mode used in this observation (see cable_delays, geometric_dlays and calibration_delays fields for more info)

FIELD.name: cable_delays
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Cable delay mode applied (see cable_delays_description for info)

FIELD.name: cable_delays_description
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Descripition of cable delay mode applied to this observation

FIELD.name: geometric_delays
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Geometric delay mode applied (see geometric_delays_description for info)

FIELD.name: geometric_delays_description
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Descripition of geometric delay mode applied to this observation

FIELD.name: calibration_delays
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Have real-time calibration delays been applied in this observation?

FIELD.name: oversampled_flag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Does this observation have oversampled coarse channels?

FIELD.name: deripple_flag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Has a de-ripple been applied to the coarse channels of this observation?

FIELD.name: deripple_params
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: If de-ripple has been applied, which de-ripple was applied?
